				\usepackage{upgreek}
				\setlength{\oddsidemargin}{-69pt}
				\begin{document}$I^{*}>0$\end{document}I∗>0. This completes the proof of (b).

(c) We have proved that \documentclass[12pt]{minimal}
				\usepackage{amsmath}
				\usepackage{wasysym} 
				\usepackage{amsfonts} 
				\usepackage{amssymb} 
				\usepackage{amsbsy}
				\usepackage{mathrsfs}
				\usepackage{upgreek}
				\setlength{\oddsidemargin}{-69pt}
				\begin{document}$x_{0}< I^{*}<x_{1}$\end{document}x0<I∗<x1. The rest of (c) follows readily, and thus the proof of the theorem is complete. □

